          {
            "text": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 64 of a 12-week money program. Week 10 theme: building unshakable money trust. The script targets the quiet residual doubt that sits underneath financial progress without announcing itself, the whisper that asks 'what if it slows down?' or 'what if I can't hold this?' The reframe moves toward deep trust in wealth as natural and lasting.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
